Hello, i am starting a new career and i though i should share the spreadsheet i have created to keep track of my progress and all the mission logs, science stuff and well pretty much everything.

Hopefully i get some feedback and maybe even give some ideas here and there.

This is like my 10th attempt to make it and it still has some critical parts that are unfinished.

Thanks, hope you like it!
